{"tid":2128182,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救］懷疑電話號碼比人偷左","createTime":"2020-07-27T19:51:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T07:41:21.000Z","uid":281422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1c1882190c441113a34ce1894b884e615d8cb5db","tid":2128182,"uid":281422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T19:51:34.000Z","msg":"呢排成日收到人打黎同我講<br />\n話咩佢地成日收到我個電話<br />\n但明明我完全唔識佢地<br />\n懷疑自己個number比人偷左<br />\n上網查都有見過有人有咁嘅情況<br />\n而我自己都成日零晨收到啲不知名call<br />\n一黎就轟炸式咁打<br />\n次次都係要block左個number先停<br />\n但係我唔想換電話號碼<br />\n有冇人話我知我應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a191eedd79daff5ff358267685dcb9ff5da7a88","tid":2128182,"uid":195915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T20:03:08.000Z","msg":"小熊來電🐻"},{"pid":"8f8150133d2f0342b4ca48d1b0c2dfb51885cebb","tid":2128182,"uid":222938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T00:18:40.000Z","msg":"有次訓醒都有個阿嬸打黎，話我朝早打過俾佢，<br />\n但我訓覺開airplane mode <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d1d7753e55e755546325f43efbcee5e61bac42","tid":2128182,"uid":281422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f8150133d2f0342b4ca48d1b0c2dfb51885cebb","tid":2128182,"uid":222938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T00:18:40.000Z","msg":"有次訓醒都有個阿嬸打黎，話我朝早打過俾佢，<br />\n但我訓覺開airplane mode <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T03:12:51.000Z","msg":"點搞好 呢排成日都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1163764fe239191cc375be51ee80b818cf0f1fb4","tid":2128182,"uid":222938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97d1d7753e55e755546325f43efbcee5e61bac42","tid":2128182,"uid":281422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f8150133d2f0342b4ca48d1b0c2dfb51885cebb","tid":2128182,"uid":222938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T00: